public class DataPackage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Client has to determine by himself if it is his turn, using currentPlayer and players Play Card: player sets currentCard with the HandCard played Question: list with Interactive.CardQuestion for client Answers: list with Answers to the questions
